软件包 pl.polidea.instrumentation

类摘要
PolideaInstrumentationTestRunner Test runner that should produce JUnit-compatible test results.
PolideaInstrumentationTestRunner.TestCaseInfo Stores information about particular test case class - containing all tests for that class.
PolideaInstrumentationTestRunner.TestInfo Stores information about single test run.
PolideaInstrumentationTestRunner.TestPackageInfo Stores information about the whole package containing multiple test cases.
